    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>String[] errorSoon = new String[n];\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>With n being how many strings it needs to hold.</p>\n\n<p>You can do that in the declaration, or do it without the String[] later on, so long as it's before you try use them.</p>\n"
