    "body" : "<p>In <strong>Java 8</strong> we can also make use of streams e.g.</p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] strings = Stream.of(\"First\", \"Second\", \"Third\").toArray(String[]::new);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>In case we already have a list of strings (<code>stringList</code>) then we can collect into string array as:</p>\n\n<pre><code>String[] strings = stringList.stream().toArray(String[]::new);\n</code></pre>\n"
