    "body" : "<pre><code>String[] arr = {\"foo\", \"bar\"};\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>If you pass a string array to a method, do:</p>\n\n<pre><code>myFunc(arr);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or do:</p>\n\n<pre><code>myFunc(new String[] {\"foo\", \"bar\"});\n</code></pre>\n"
